title: No serious injuries reported after car drives into Volo sandwich shop
text: No serious injuries reported after car drives into Volo sandwich shop Car crashes into Jimmy John's Joe Shuman / News-Sun Lake County Sheriff's police and the Fox Lake Fire Department responded to a Jimmy John's at 2745 Hartigan Road in Volo where a car drove through the front of the building Thursday afternoon.
